New Release! The Ultimate Italian "One-Off" 🔥 | A 1:8 scale beast built from 3300+ pieces and over 60cm long. 

Finished in custom silver grey metallic, it features a fully functional V12 engine, remote-controlled scissor doors, drive, steering, adjustable ride height, spoiler, and even a smoke effect device. LED lights, carbon fiber accents, custom rims… every detail screams performance.

Only available at 24builds.com 🚀🚀
